3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20crayfish%20and%20glow-worms%2C%20protected%20plants%20and%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.des.qld.gov.au%2Four-department%2Fnews-media%2Fmediareleases%2Fselfish-selfies-put-carnarvon-rock-art-at-risk%5C%22%3EFirst%20Nations%20rock%20art%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Selfies%20have%20even%20become%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Faustralia-news%2F2022%2Fsep%2F28%2Fcanola-field-selfies-australian-farmers-warn-tourists-against-dangerous-social-media-trend%5C%22%3Ebiosecurity%20threat.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpare%20a%20thought%20for%20our%20land%20managers%2C%20tasked%20with%20caring%20for%20the%20natural%20places%20sometimes%20despoiled%20for%20a%20photo%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fonlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1111%2F1742-6723.14219%5C%22%3Eemergency%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%20entrusted%20with%20rescuing%20selfie-seekers.%20As%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1080%2F13683500.2023.2248349%5C%22%3Eour%20new%20research%20has%20found%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Australia%E2%80%99s%20land%20managers%20are%20often%20at%20their%20wit%E2%80%99s%20end%20trying%20to%20keep%20people%20safe%20in%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%3F%20Fences%20and%20warning%20signs%20don%E2%80%99t%20work%20well.%20Hardcore%20selfie-seekers%20jump%20the%20fence%20and%20perch%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20cliff%20to%20get%20the%20shot.%20We%20may%20well%20need%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rt.com%2Frussia%2F272200-russia-selfie-police-twitter%2F%5C%22%3Eselfie%20educational%20campaigns%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESelfies%20make%20a%20new%20brand%20of%20tourist%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20tourism%20is%20drastically%20changing%20who%20and%20how%20many%20of%20us%20go%20to%20places%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nationalparks.nsw.gov.au%2Fthings-to-do%2Flookouts%2Ffigure-eight-pools%5C%22%3EFigure%20Eight%20Pools%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Sydney%E2%80%99s%20Royal%20National%20Park%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fparks.des.qld.gov.au%2Fparks%2Fwooroonooran-josephine-falls%5C%22%3EJosephine%20Falls%3C%2Fa%3E%20not%20far%20from%20Cairns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20one%20land%20manager%20told%20us%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20noticed%20a%20massive%20increase%20in%20the%20number%20of%20people%2C%20and%20the%20kind%20of%20visitor%20that%20we%20were%20getting.%20We%E2%80%99re%20getting%20a%20lot%20more%20people%20who%20are%20maybe%20urban%20based%2C%20didn%E2%80%99t%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20in%20national%20parks%2C%20weren%E2%80%99t%20particularly%20familiar%20with%20the%20concept%20of%20bushwalking.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELand%20managers%20told%20us%20these%20new%20kinds%20of%20tourist%20were%20motivated%20to%20seek%20out%20photos%20and%20selfies.%20The%20problem%20was%2C%20many%20were%20willing%20to%20ignore%20warning%20signs%20or%20bans%20on%20drones%20to%20get%20their%20photos.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20know%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20all%20just%20to%20get%20that%20photo%2C%20really.%20That%E2%80%99s%20it.%20People%20definitely%2C%20more%20so%20now%20than%20ever%2C%20I%20think%2C%20are%20coming%20for%20the%20photo.%20They%E2%80%99re%20not%20coming%20for%20a%20bushwalk%20and%20to%20look%20around%20at%20the%20trees%20and%20to%20experience%20nature.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDrone%20use%20is%20common%2C%20even%20when%20it%20is%20banned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20break%20the%20Civil%20Aviation%20Safety%20Authority%20(CASA)%20rules%20%5Bon%20drones%5D%2C%20every%20flipping%20day%2C%20they%20annoy%20the%20people%2C%20the%20guests%2C%20the%20wildlife%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%20I%E2%80%99ve%20got%20eight%20crashed%20drones%20in%20the%20park%20currently%20%5Brisking%5D%20environmental%20harm%20to%20the%20park%20if%20they%20catch%20fire%20or%20the%20batteries%20leak%20in%20the%20World%20Heritage%20area%2C%20in%20the%20creeks%20where%20the%20rare%20crayfish%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20other%20land%20managers%2C%20the%20challenge%20is%20the%20damage%20to%20the%20environment.%20Plants%20get%20trampled%2C%20wildlife%20disturbed%2C%20and%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20delicate%20ecosystems%20suffer%20long-term%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSomeone%20goes%20swimming%2C%20puts%20it%20on%20social%20media%20and%20suddenly%20there%E2%80%99s%20100%20people%20a%20day%20coming%20to%20go%20wild%20swimming%20where%20the%20platypus%20and%20the%20glow-worms%20live.%20And%20in%20a%20wet%20year%2C%20suddenly%20all%20the%20vegetation%20around%20the%20rock%20pool%20is%20trampled%2C%20it%20turns%20into%20a%20muddy%20mess.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMainstream%20tourism%20bodies%20can%20make%20the%20problem%20worse%20by%20promoting%20social%20media%20hotspot%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20horrified%20the%20other%20day%20noticing%20promotions%20for%20these%20Figure%20Eight%20pools.%20I%20just%20thought%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%E2%80%99ve%20gotta%20be%20kidding%20me.%20How%20many%20times%20have%20we%20told%20the%20tourism%20industry%20to%20stop%20it%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESafe%20selfies%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20the%20thorniest%20challenge%20for%20land%20managers%20is%20accommodating%20increased%20interest%20while%20keeping%20people%20safe.%20That%E2%80%99s%20because%20selfie-seekers%20sometimes%20deliberately%20avoid%20safety%20measures%20like%20fences.%20As%20one%20land%20manager%20told%20us%3A%20%E2%80%9CThey%20want%20to%20get%20a%20photo%20without%20a%20fence%20in%20it.%20Look%20at%20me%20with%20my%20toes%20over%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20crumbly%20sandstone%20cliff.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20land%20managers%20are%20working%20to%20assist%20this%20new%20demand%20by%20reshaping%20nature%20to%20make%20better%20scenery%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0and%20keep%20visitors%20safer.%20At%20Moran%20Falls%20in%20Queensland%E2%80%99s%20Lamington%20National%20Park%2C%20a%20famous%20view%20across%20the%20gorge%20had%20been%20obscured%20by%20vegetation.%20That%20drove%20some%20visitors%20to%20jump%20the%20fence%20at%20the%20viewing%20platform%20and%20stand%20directly%20on%20top%20of%20a%20very%20tall%20cliff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20solution%2C%20land%20managers%20got%20an%20arborist%20to%20trim%20the%20trees%20blocking%20the%20view%20and%20then%20use%20the%20fallen%20limbs%20to%20hide%20the%20goat%20track%20made%20by%20selfie-seekers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20we%20improved%20the%20view%20and%20the%20photo%20shot%2C%20people%20were%20happy%20to%20take%20the%20photo%20from%20the%20platform.%20But%20when%20the%20view%20was%20impeded%20from%20the%20platform%2C%20they%20would%20undertake%20risky%20behaviour%20and%20stand%20on%20top%20of%20a%20300ft%20cliff%2C%20right%20on%20the%20edge%2C%20to%20get%20the%20photo.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20do%20traditional%20measures%20like%20signs%20and%20warnings%20often%20prove%20ineffective%3F%20The%20answer%20may%20lie%20in%20social%20validation.%20For%20many%2C%20the%20risk%20seems%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscholars.fhsu.edu%2Fcgi%2Fviewcontent.cgi%3Farticle%3D4234%26context%3Dtheses%5C%22%3Eworth%20the%20reward%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20it%20means%20garnering%20admiration%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENature-based%20content%20on%20platforms%20like%20Instagram%20and%20TikTok%20often%20performs%20very%20well%2C%20giving%20other%20would-be%20influencers%20the%20incentive%20to%20seek%20out%20new%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20can%20we%20do%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELand%20managers%20have%20repeatedly%20told%20us%20signs%20aren%E2%80%99t%20working%20for%20these%20new%20tourists.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20an%20urgent%20need%20to%20communicate%20risk%20and%20safety%20information%20in%20novel%20ways%20which%20resonate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tools%20land%20managers%20have%20are%20often%20preventive%20%E2%80%93%20barriers%2C%20boardwalks%20and%20signs%2C%20coupled%20with%20punitive%20measures%20such%20as%20fines.%20But%20this%20isn%E2%80%99t%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetter%20risk%20communication%2C%20as%20New%20South%20Wales%20authorities%20are%20doing%20with%20time-sensitive%20risk%20warnings%20for%20Figure%20Eight%20Pools%2C%20may%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F24165017%2Ffile-20230823-19-czywog.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221050%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F24165017%2Ffile-20230823-19-czywog.png%201050w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F24165017%2Ffile-20230823-19-czywog-263x300.png%20263w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F24165017%2Ffile-20230823-19-czywog-896x1024.png%20896w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-669629%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EFigure%20Eight%20Pools%20are%20on%20a%20rock%20platform%20which%20is%20inundated%20at%20high%20tide.%20This%20risk%20communication%20approach%20has%20promise.%20Photo%3A%20NSW%20National%20Parks%20and%20Wildlife%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20research%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1080%2F13683500.2023.2248349%5C%22%3Epoints%20to%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20need%20for%20fresh%20strategies%20to%20tackle%20social%20media%20hotspots%20and%20selfie-seeking%20by%20understanding%20what%20drives%20social%20media%20tourists%2C%20improving%20risk%20communication%20and%20developing%20partnerships.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20problem%20has%20been%20created%20by%20the%20confluence%20of%20social%20media%20and%20human%20psychology.%20It%20may%20well%20be%20that%20the%20solution%20lies%20in%20the%20same%20intersection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ER