ann%20Khurrana's%20%3Cem%3EAn%20Action%20Hero%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EDoctor%20G%3C%2Fem%3E%20released%20last%20year%20and%20both%20the%20movies%20tanked%20at%20the%20box%20office.%20Amid%20%3Cem%3EGadar%202%3C%2Fem%3E%20wave%2C%20which%20doesn't%20seem%20to%20slow%20down%20in%20near%20future%2C%20Ayushmann%20Khurrana%20was%20asked%20by%20The%20Indian%20Express%20if%20he%20feels%20jittery%20about%20the%20box%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%3Cem%3E%20Vicky%20Donor%3C%2Fem%3E%20actor%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20good%20to%20be%20nervous%2C%20it%20feels%20like%20your%2010th%20board%20exams%20results%20are%20coming%20out%2C%20it%20is%20that%20kind%20of%20feeling.%26quot%3B%20Ayushmann%20called%20%3Cem%3EDream%20Girl%202%3C%2Fem%3E%20his%20%26quot%3Bmost%20massy%20film%26quot%3B%20and%20he%20believes%20it%20will%20pull%20audience%20in%20the%20theatres.%20Ayushmann%20Khurrana%20said%20to%20the%20Indian%20Express%2C%20%26quot%3BBut%20at%20the%20same%20time%20this%20has%20been%20my%20most%20massy%20film%20and%20it%20has%20also%20penetrated%20in%20two%20tier%20and%20three%20tier%20cities%2C%20So%20I%20am%20most%20excited%20about%20this%20one%20as%20a%20theatrical%20palette%2C%20it's%20for%20wider%20audience%2C%20you've%20ticked%20all%20the%20right%20boxes%20and%20it's%20also%20a%20sequel%2C%20so%20this%20is%20the%20safest%20of%20all%20because%20it's%20a%20hard%20core%20family%20entertainer.%20It's%20a%20fun%20film.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaaj%20Shaandilyaa%20has%20directed%20%3Cem%3EDream%20Girl%202%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20Ektaa%20R%20Kapoor%20has%20produced%20it.%20The%20movie%20stars%20Manjot%20Singh%2C%20Rajpal%20Yadav%2C%20Paresh%20Rawal%2C%20Asrani%2C%20Manoj%20Joshi%2C%20Seema%20Pahwa%20and%20Vijay%20Raaz%20in%20supporting%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692877680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fe8964h2g_aayushman-_625x300_24_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fayushmann