hi%20area%2C%20like%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20Khan%20Market%2C%20Mandi%20House%20and%20Central%20Secretariat%20are%20expected%20to%20remain%20closed%20for%20three%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETraffic%20restrictions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20officials%2C%20traffic%20will%20be%20restricted%20for%20a%20specific%20time%20in%20some%20areas%20of%20Delhi.%20This%20will%20be%20done%20in%20order%20to%20avoid%20jams%20and%20keeping%20in%20view%20the%20security%20of%20the%20visiting%20VVIPs.%20Shopping%20malls%20and%20markets%20in%20certain%20areas%20will%20also%20be%20closed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20areas%20with%20VVIP%20movement%2C%20buses%20will%20either%20be%20stopped%20or%20alternate%20routes%20given.%20Interstate%20bus%20service%20can%20be%20rescheduled%20around%20Delhi%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20officials%20said%20that%20care%20will%20be%20taken%20to%20ensure%20that%20there%20is%20no%20impact%20on%20the%20hospital%20and%20emergency%20services%2C%20as%20well%20as%20those%20travelling%20by%20rail%20and%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPublic%20holiday%20in%20Delhi%20for%203%20days%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20Delhi%20government%20and%20private%20offices%2C%20and%20educational%20institutions%2C%20including%20schools%20and%20colleges%2C%20will%20remain%20closed%20from%20September%208-10%2C%20as%20per%20a%20notification%20issued%20by%20the%20General%20Administration%20Department%20(GAD)%20of%20the%20Delhi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20See%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fin-10-pics-how-delhi-is-being-decked-up-for-g20-summit-4318708%5C%22%3E10%20New%20Features%20In%20Delhi%20Ahead%20Of%20G-20%20In%20Pics%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20commercial%20banks%20and%20financial%20institutions%20situated%20within%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%20New%20Delhi%20Police%20District%2C%20which%20come%20under%20the%20purview%20of%20Section%2025%20