22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian%20budget%20airline%20SpiceJet%20told%20a%20court%20on%20Thursday%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bstruggling%20to%20stay%20afloat%26quot%3B%2C%20as%20it%20was%20ordered%20to%20make%20a%20payment%20to%20its%20former%20owner%20over%20money%20owed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%20SpiceJet%20lost%20an%20arbitration%20case%20arising%20out%20of%20share%20transfers%20from%20former%20owner%20Kalanithi%20Maran%20to%20the%20company's%20new%20management%20in%202015%2C%20making%20the%20airline%20liable%20to%20pay%20%2470%20million%20plus%20interest.%20Maran%20later%20took%20SpiceJet%20to%20court%20saying%20he%20was%20still%20owed%20%2448%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20hearing%20on%20Thursday%20on%20Maran's%20case%20demanding%20the%20dues%2C%20SpiceJet%20said%20it%20was%20struggling%20financially.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20struggling%20to%20stay%20afloat%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20airline's%20lawyer%20Amit%20Sibal%20told%20the%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpiceJet%20offered%20to%20deposit%20750%20million%20rupees%20(%249.08%20million)%20within%2010%20days%2C%20but%20the%20judge%20ordered%20the%20airline%20to%20pay%201%20billion%20rupees%20(%2412%20million)%20by%20Sept.%2010%20and%20warned%20it%20could%20consider%20seizing%20the%20company's%20assets%20to%20recover%20the%20dues%2C%20if%20it%20fails%20to%20comply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpiceJet%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20it%20would%20honour%20the%20court%20order%20and%20%26quot%3Bmake%20the%20specified%20payment%20within%20the%20prescribed%20timeframe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20comes%20days%20after%20India's%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20in%20a%20separate%20case%2C%20asked%20SpiceJet's%20Managing%20Director%20Ajay%20Singh%20to%20appear%20in%20court%20and%20defend%20allegations%20by%20Credit%20Suisse%20claiming%20certain%20unpaid%20dues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20case%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20case%20will%20next%20be%20hear