gh-court-it-is-struggling-to-stay-afloat-4325823%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%2040%25%20rout%20in%20Apple%20bonds%20is%20signaling%20trouble%20for%20bank%20balance%20sheets%20with%20big%20debt%20holdings%2C%20markets%20guru%20Larry%20McDonald%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222832%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Larry%20McDonald%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F646742a8cd3a9c0019184c49%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222124%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELarry%20McDonald.%3Cp%3ELarry%20McDonald%2FThe%20Bear%20Traps%20Report%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%2040%25%20plunge%20in%20Apple's%20bonds%20highlights%20the%20risks%20facing%20banks'%20debt%20portfolios%2C%20according%20to%20Larry%20McDonald.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20markets%20guru%20highlighted%20risks%20tied%20to%20mortgage-backed%20securities%2C%20which%20are%20on%20track%20for%20a%20third%20annual%20decline.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESilicon%20Valley%20Bank's%20collapse%20in%20March%2C%20which%20set%20off%20a%20wave%20of%20banking%20turmoil%2C%20was%20caused%20by%20the%20losses%20on%20its%20bond%20portfolio.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EApple's%20long-term%20bonds%20have%20lost%2040%25%20of%20their%20value%20since%20late%202020%20thanks%20to%20the%20Federal%20Reserve's%20interest-rate%20increases%20-%20and%20that's%20highlighting%20the%20mounting%20risks%20for%20banks%20from%20their%20debt%20holdings%2C%20according%20to%20Larry%20McDonald.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20price%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fbonds%2Fapple_incdl-notes_202020-60-bond-2060-us037833ea41%5C%22%3EApple's%202.55%25%20debt%20due%20in%202060%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20slumped%20to%20about%20%2461.80%20from%20%24100.59%20at%20the%20end%20of%202020.%20The%20bulk%20of%20the%20declines%20came%20since%20early%202022%2C%20when%20the%20US%20central%20bank%20started%20raising%20rates%20to%20quell%20inflation.%20The%20Fed%20has%20lifted%20its%20benchmark%20rate%20by%20more%20than%20500%20basis%20points%20since%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBonds%20paying%20a%20fixed%20coupon%20rate%20become%20less%20attractive%20to%20investors%20as%20market%20interest%20rates%20move%20higher%2C%20causing%20the%20price%20of%20such%20securities%20to%20fall.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20shocking%20collapse%20of%20Silicon%20Valley%20Bank%20was%20triggered%20by%20massive%20losses%20arising%20from%20its%20portfolio%20of%20Treasuries%2C%20and%20the%20event%20set%20off%20a%20wave%20of%20turmoil%20across%20the%20global%20banking%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInterest%20rates%20up%20---%20bonds%20prices%20down.%20%241%20million%20invested%20in%20this%20Apple%20AAPL%20bond%20is%20now%20worth%20%24600k%2C%20duration%20risk%20is%20on%20stage%20here.%20Now%20think%20of%20all%20those%20mortgage-backed%20securities%20on%20bank%20balance%20sheets%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%26quot%3BBear%20Traps%20Report%26quot%3B%20founder%20said%20in%20a%20Wednesday%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FConvertbond%2Fstatus%2F1694134926868627611%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMortgage-backed%20securities%2C%20or%20MBS%2C%20which%20are%20homebuyers'%20loans%20repacked%20as%20bonds%2C%20have%20also%20seen%20sharp%20declines%20in%20recent%20years.%20BlackRock's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fetfs%2Fishares-mbs-etf-us4642885887%5C%22%3EiShares%20MBS%20exchange-traded%20fund%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20shed%20more%20than%2018%25%20of%20its%20value%20since%20hitting%20a%202020%20peak.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcDonald%20seemed%20to%20suggest%20that%20if%20the%20bonds%20of%20top-rated%20companies%20such%20as%20Apple%20could%20take%20such%20a%20knock%20from%20rising%20interest%20rates%2C%20declines%20in%20the%20broader%20debt%20market%20could%20be%20sizable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMBS%20securities%20are%20closely%20related%20t