C%20more%20importantly%2C%20night%20temperatures%20can%20reach%20a%20destructive%20-208%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%20or%20-%20133%20degrees%20Celsius%20and%20the%20rover%2C%20the%20lander%20and%20the%20payloads%20will%20likely%20have%20severe%20trouble%20operating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-chandrayaan-3-updates-pragyan-rover-vikram-lander-pragyan-at-work-vikram-keeps-watch-busy-day-for-chandrayaan-3-duo-4324431%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topstories%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAs%20Nation%20Celebrates%2C%20Chandrayaan-3's%20Lander-Rover%20Start%20Busy%20Day%20At%20Moon%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20this%20time%2C%20the%20rover%20will%20be%20touch%20with%20the%20lander%20and%20that%20will%20relay%20data%20back%20to%20ISRO's%20mission%20command%20centre.%20ISRO%20will%20have%20no%20direct%20link%20with%20the%20rover%20for%20this%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EThe%20Landing%20Date%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20legion%20of%20scientists%20at%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20planned%20Chandrayaan-3's%20landing%20date%20with%20the%20same%20accuracy%20and%20precision%20that%20helped%20them%20land%20the%201%2C752%20kg%20Vikram%20lander%20(with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fpragyan-rover%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPragyan%20rover%3C%2Fa%3E%20inside)%20nearly%20400%2C000%20km%20from%20Earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-soft-landing-moon-vikram-lander-pragyan-rover-chandrayaan-3-makes-history-lands-on-moon-relive-the-final-20-minutes-4322959%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHow%20Chandrayaan-3's%20Final%20%26quot%3B20%20Minutes%20Of%20Terror%26quot%3B%20Played%20Out%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAugust%2023%20was%20the%20start%20of%20one%20lunar%20day%2Fnight%20cycle%2C%20which%20was%20why%20that%20date%20was%20picked%20as%20the%20landing%20date.%20If%20Vikram%20failed%20to%20touch%20down%20on%20that%20day%2C%20ISRO%20had%20a%20back-up%20plan%20-%20land%20on%20August%2024.%20If%20there%20was%20still%20no%20touch%20down%20(and%20the%20lander%20was%20undamaged)%2C%20ISRO%20reportedly%20planned%20to%20try%20again%2029%20days%20later%20-%20after%20a%20full%20day%2Fnight%20cycle%20on%20the%20moon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWhy%20The%20Lunar%20South%20Pole%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fchandrayaan~3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChandrayaan-3%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20special%20as%20no%20other%20spacecraft%20has%20been%20able%20to%20achieve%20a%20soft%20landing%20near%20the%20Moon's%20South%20Pole.%20This%20area%20-%20far%20from%20the%20equatorial%20region%20targeted%20by%20other%20missions%2C%20including%20NASA's%20crewed%20Apollo%20landings%20-%20is%20full%20of%20craters%20and%20deep%20trenches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20findings%20from%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20mission%20could%20advance%20and%20expand%20knowledge%20of%20lunar%20water%20ice%2C%20potentially%20one%20of%20the%20moon's%20most%20valuable%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3ESo%20What%20Happens%20To%20The%20Lunar%20Modules%20After%20Mission%20Completion%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeither%20the%20Vikram%20lander%20nor%20the%20Pragyan%20rover%20will%20return%20to%20Earth%20-%20despite%20what%20some%20Indian%20lawmakers%20may%20believe.%20And%20neither%20will%20the%20propulsion%20module%20that%20delivered%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-mission-isro-chief-chose-south-pole-because-isro-chief-on-chandrayaan-3-prime-objectives-4324963%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BChose%20South%20Pole%20Because...%26quot%3B%3A%20ISRO%20Chief%20On%20Chandrayaan-3's%20Prime%20Objectives%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20completion%20of%20their%20respective%20experiments%20both%20the%20lander%20and%20rover%20will%20remain%20on%20the%20Moon.%20They%20will%20not%20be%20functional%20during%20the%20lunar%20night%20and%20while%20there%20is%20no%20plan%20to%20revive%20them%20after%20that%20period%2C%20ISRO%20is%20hopeful%20both%20will%20survive%20the%20long%20night%20and%20start%20up%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EThe%20Chandrayaan-3%20Mission%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rs%20600%20crore-Chandrayaan-3%20mission%20was%20launched%20from%20the%20Satish%20Dhawan%20Space%20Centre%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh's%20Sriharikota%20on%20July%2014%2C%20piggybacking%20on%20a%20Launch%20Vehicle%20Mark-III%20(LVM-3)%20rocket.%20The%20journey%20to%20the%20Moon%20took%2041%20days%20and%2C%20significantly%2C%20was%20completed%20just%20days%20after%20a%20Russian%20spacecraft%20attempting%20a%20similar%20outcome%20crashed%20after%20spinning%20out%20of%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692875460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Ftk24u1sg_rover-pragyan_650x400_23_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-moon-soft-landing-pragyan-rover-vikram-lander-14-earth-days-4325557%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Vikram%20lander%20and%20Pragyan%20rover%20will%20have%2014%20Earth%20days%20to%20gather%20scientific%20data%20from%20the%20Moon's%20surface%20and%20atmosphere%2C%20after%20which%20there%20will%20be%20a%20lunar%20night%20for%20another%2014%20Earth%20days.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-moon-soft-landing-pragyan-rover-vikram-lander-14-earth-days-4325557%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-moon-soft-landing-pragyan-rover-vikram-lander-14-earth-days-4325557%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.