-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_top%5C%22%3Efor%20the%20first%20time%20in%20both%20Japan%20and%20Romania%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20this%20was%20the%20first%20time%20the%20AC-130%20operated%20in%20Australia%2C%20the%20aircraft%20could%20be%20based%20in%20the%20area%20if%20tensions%20with%20China%20continue%20to%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AC-130's%20primary%20mission%20sets%20are%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fair-force-retiring-a10-amid-dobuts-about-close-air-support-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclose%20air%20support%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20air%20interdiction%2C%20and%20armed%20reconnaissance.%20Essentially%2C%20the%20AC-130%20is%20an%20aerial%20artillery%20platform%20that%20flies%20over%20a%20target%20slowly%20and%20fires%20cannons%20and%20precision%20munitions%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ac130-gunship-crews-use-their-green-beam-lasers-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_top%5C%22%3Ewith%20deadly%20accuracy%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20AC-130%20is%20really%20only%20suited%20for%20operations%20in%20areas%20where%20the%20US%20and%20its%20allies%20have%20established%20air%20superiority%2C%20as%20its%20bulky%20size%20and%20relatively%20slow%20speed%20leave%20it%20vulnerable%20to%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20beloved%20aircraft%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22AC-130J%20Australia%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e64a79912f290019a9c974%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221331%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20US%20Air%20Force%20weapon%20systems%20operator%20gives%20a%20tour%20of%20an%20AC-130J%20to%20Australian%20Air%20Force%20cadets%20at%20Royal%20Australian%20Air%20Force%20Base%20Richmond%20during%20Talisman%20Sabre%20in%20July.%3Cp%3EUS%20Air%20Force%2FSenior%20Airman%20Alexcia%20Givens%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlongside%20a%20few%20other%20aircraf