k%20told%20Reuters%20that%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Bno%20indication%20that%20there%20was%20anything%20wrong%20with%20this%20aircraft%26quot%3B%20prior%20to%20its%20dramatic%20drop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F812c9da3-80f2-4fe1-8fad-0b4441d1977a%5C%22%3EThe%20Financial%20Times%20noted%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20plume%20trailing%20the%20plane%20resembled%20shots%20fired%20from%20anti-aircraft%20defenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20theory%20was%20echoed%20in%20a%20post%20on%20Grey%20Zone%2C%20a%20Telegram%20channel%20linked%20to%20the%20Wagner%20group%2C%20which%20alleged%20that%20Russia's%20anti-aircraft%20defenses%20had%20shot%20down%20the%20plane%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20social%20media%20channel%20also%20claimed%20that%20residents%20near%20the%20crash%20heard%20%26quot%3Btwo%20bursts%20of%20characteristic%20air%20defense%20fire%26quot%3B%20before%20the%20crash%2C%20per%20the%20Financial%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Reuters%2C%20unnamed%20Russian%20media%20sources%20also%20backed%20the%20notion%20that%20the%20plane%20had%20been%20shot%20down%20by%20one%20or%20more%20surface-to-air%20missiles%2C%20though%20the%20news%20agency%20was%20unable%20to%20confirm%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20theory%20is%20that%20some%20kind%20of%20bomb%20was%20on%20the%20plane.%20John%20Sawers%2C%20the%20former%20head%20of%20Britain's%20MI6%20spy%20agency%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Flive%2Fworld-66599774%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20the%20BBC%20Thursday%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20thought%20%26quot%3Bthere%20was%20some%20device%20on%20board%20that%20brought%20the%20plane%20down%20suddenly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussian%20investigators%20have%20opened%20a%20probe%20into%20the%20incident.%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20suggested%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20was%20likely%20behind%20the%20crash%2C%20though%20he%20didn't%20speak%20with%20certainty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20may%20recall%2C%20I%20was%20asked%20about%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2023%2F08%2F23%2Feurope%2Frussia-wagner-prigozhin-plane-crash-intl%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BI%20said%20I%20would%20be%20careful%20what%20I%20rode%20in.%20I%20don't%20know%20for%20a%20fact%20what%20happened%2C%20but%20I'm%20not%20surprised.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUK%20defense%20sources%20also%20told%20the%20BBC%20that%20the%20plane%20was%20most%20likely%20brought%20down%20by%20the%20Russian%20government%2C%20placing%20the%20blame%20on%20Russia's%20Federal%20Security%20Service%20(FSB).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLikely%20to%20strengthen%20position%20of%20Prigozhin's%20enemies%3A%20Shoigu%20and%20Gerasimov%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FFrankRGardner%2Fstatus%2F1694618676727583184%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Esaid%20the%20BBC's%20Security%20Correspondent%20Frank%20Gardner%20in%20a%20tweet.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fplane-crash-yevgeny-prigozhin-russia-appeared-fine-until-last-seconds-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692873221000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e724cea7adf7001906c97e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fplane-crash-yevgeny-prigozhin-russia-appeared-fine-until-last-seconds-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20jet%20carrying%20Yevgeny%20Prigozhin%20was%20flying%20normally%20until%20it%20made%20a%20%26quot%3Bsudden%20downward%20vertical%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20last%2030%20seconds%2C%20Reuters%20reported.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jzitser%40businessinsider.com%20(Joshua%20Zitser)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A33%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fplane-crash-yevgeny-prigozhin-russia-appeared-fine-until-last-seconds-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22With%20an%20Export%20Duty%20on%20Onions%2C%20It's%20Clear%20How%20Much%20the%20Government%20Prioritises%20Farmers'%20Income%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F14102358%2F5560910594_bdc7d1c175_c.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20grappling%20with%20a%20surge%20in%20tomato%20prices%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20decided%20to%20impose%2040%25%20export%20duty%20on%20onions%20until%20December.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20time%20that%20export%20duty%20has%20been%20imposed%20on%20onions.%20This%20ruins%20any%20chance%20of%20export.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EConsumer%20interest%20has%20once%20more%20taken%20priority%20over%20farmers%E2%80%99%20income.%20When%20farmers%20started%20agitating%2C%20the%20government%20had%20announced%20that%202%20lakh%20tonnes%20onions%20would%20be%20procured%20at%20Rs%202%2C410%20per%20quintal.%20Some%20would%20say%20that%20is%20the%20Minimum%20Support%20Price%20(MSP)%20for%20onions%2C%20a%20new%20tradition%20that%20farmers%20would%20hope%20will%20continue%20for%20other%20crops%20when%20farm%20gate%20prices%20crash.%20%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20about%2019.4%20lakh%20hectares%20under%20onion%2C%20India%20grew%20316.8%20lakh%20tonnes%20of%20onion%20in%202021-22.%20Onion%20production%20in%202022-23%20is%20estimated%20to%20be%20310%20lakh%20tonnes.%20Maharashtra%20continues%20to%20be%20the%20dominant%20producer%20of%20onions%2C%20accounting%20for%2040.7%25%20of%20domestic%20production%20(126.4%20lakh%20tonnes)%20while%2016.6%25%20comes%20from%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20(51.5%20lakh%20tonnes).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EFactors%20affecting%20sensitivity%20of%20onions%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnion%20is%20a%20climate%20sensitive%20crop%20as%20winter%20frost%2C%20high%20summer%20temperatures%20and%20untimely%20rainfall%20can%20hamper%20its%20yield.%20Untimely%20rains%20in%20April%20damaged%20the%20crop.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fagricoop.nic.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FMonthly%2520Report%2520on%2520Onion%2520for%2520May%252C%25202018.pdf%5C%22%3EOnions%20are%20consumed%20round%20the%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%2060-65%25%20production%20is%20in%20Rabi%20(sown%20in%20November-December%20and%20harvested%20in%20April).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKharif%20onion%20is%20sown%20in%20June-July%20and%20is%20harvested%20in%20October-November.%20The%20late%20Kharif%20crop%20is%20sown%20in%20September-October%20and%20is%20harvested%20in%20December-January.%20Kharif%20and%20later%20Kharif%20produce%20about%2020%20percent%20each.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERabi%20onions%20are%20stored%20for%20consumption%20between%20June-September.%20The%20farmers%20have%20also%20created%20storage%20structures%20under%20various%20schemes%20of%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202015-16%2C%20Modi%20government%20set%20up%20a%20Price%20Stabilisation%20Fund%20(PSF)%20that%20could%20be%20used%20to%20procure%20agricultural%20produce%20at%20market%20prices.%20In%20the%20first%20year%20itself%2C%20Small%20Farmers%E2%80%99%20Agri-Business%20Consortium%20and%20National%20Agricultural%20Cooperative%20Marketing%20Federation%20of%20India%20Ltd.%20(NAFED)%20procured%20onions%20which%20were%20later%20sold%20in%20Delhi%20and%20other%20places%20through%20Mother%20Dairy.%20PSF%20has%20since%20been%20used%20to%20create%20buffer%20stock%20of%20onion%20and%20pulses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIronically%2C%20for%202023-24%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiabudget.gov.in%2Fdoc%2Feb%2Fvol1.pdf%5C%22%3Ethe%20Union%20budget%20provides%20only%20a%20token%20amount%20of%20Rs%201%20lakh%20for%20PSF%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPrice%20outlook%20for%202023-24%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20fluctuation%20in%20price%20realisation%20by%20farmers.%20Figure%201%20shows%20wholesale%20prices%20of%20onion%20of%20Lasalgaon%2C%20Maharashtra%20and%20Azadpur%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EMandi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Delhi.%20The%20wholesale%20prices%20of%20onion%20stood%20at%20only%20Rs%2013.25%20per%20kilogram%20(kg)%20in%20July%202023%20in%20Lasalgaon%20and%20it%20was%20Rs%2014.4%20per%20kg%20in%20Azadpur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20retail%20price%20of%20onion%20in%20New%20Delhi%20was%20Rs%2032.3%20per%20kg%20in%20July%202023%2C%20up%20from%20Rs%2026%20per%20kg%20in%20June%202023.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20price%20rise%20seems%20to%20have%20persuaded%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Fnation%2Fgovernment-procures-3-lakh-tonnes-of-onion-for-buffer-stock-526191%5C%22%3Erelease%20stock%20from%20onions%3C%2Fa%3E%20procured%20under%20PSF.%20On%20August%2011%2C%20the%20government%20announced%20sale%20of%20onion%20from%20its%20buffer%20stock.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EFigure%201%3A%20Wholesale%20and%20retail%20prices%20of%20onions%20at%20Lasalgaon%20(the%20largest%20wholesale%20onion%20market)%20and%20Delhi%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F24151813%2FScreenshot-2023-08-24-at-3.17.50-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F24151813%2FScreenshot