.%20It%20was%20a%20quick%20form%20that%20took%20about%20five%20minutes%20for%20borrowers%20to%20fill%20out%2C%20simply%20requiring%20their%20names%2C%20contact%20information%2C%20and%20Social%20Security%20number%20%E2%80%94%20and%20within%20weeks%2C%2026%20million%20borrowers%20submitted%20the%20application%2C%20and%20the%20Education%20Department%20approved%2016%20million%20of%20them%20for%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20that%20momentum%20came%20to%20a%20halt%20in%20November%2C%20when%20two%20conservative-backed%20lawsuits%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flawsuits-delay-biden-student-loan-debt-forgiveness-where-they-stand-2022-10%5C%22%3Esucceeded%20in%20blocking%C2%A0implementation%20of%20the%20relief%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20cases%20eventually%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwill-supreme-court-block-student-loan-debt-forgiveness-major-takeaways-2023-2%5C%22%3Ewent%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20for%20oral%20arguments%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20February%2C%20and%20in%20June%2C%20the%20high%20court%20ultimately%20ruled%20that%20one%20of%20the%20cases%20had%20merit%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-blocked-supreme-court-strikes-down-debt-cancellation-2023-5%5C%22%3Eand%20struck%20the%20debt%20relief%20down%3C%2Fa%3E.%20While%20some%20conservative%20groups%20and%20Republican%20lawmakers%20celebrated%20the%20decision%2C%20borrowers%20were%20defeated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20some%20apprehension%20about%20Biden's%20first%20plan%20for%20relief%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20borrower%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-student-debt-not-excited-biden-new-loan-forgiveness-2023-7%5C%22%3Epreviously%20told%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20sure%20enough%2C%20that's%20exactly%20what%20happened.%20It%20did%20go%20all%20the%20way%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20was%20deemed%20ineligible.%20So%20it's%20been%20a%20roller%20co