ding%20workforce%2C%20Rishi%20Sunak%20failed%20to%20declare%20that%20his%20wife%20held%20shares%20in%20one%20of%20six%20childminding%20agencies%20selected%20by%20the%20government%20to%20provide%20its%20new%20members%20with%20an%20enhanced%20financial%20incentive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERishi%20Sunak%2C%2043%2C%20told%20the%20parliamentary%20watchdog%20that%20he%20had%20declared%20the%20interest%20on%20the%20Ministerial%20Register%20and%20Greenberg%20concluded%20that%20he%20was%20satisfied%20that%20Rishi%20Sunak%20had%20confused%20the%20concept%20of%20registration%20with%20the%20concept%20of%20declaration%20of%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20formed%20the%20view%20that%20the%20failure%20to%20declare%20arose%20out%20of%20this%20confusion%20and%20was%20accordingly%20inadvertent%20on%20the%20part%20of%20Mr%20Sunak%2C%26quot%3B%20noted%20Greenberg%20in%20his%20inquiry%20report%20released%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20view%20of%20this%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20conclude%20my%20inquiry%20by%20way%20of%20the%20rectification%20procedure%20available%20to%20me%20under%20Standing%20Order%20No.%20150%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20which%20stops%20short%20of%20a%20formal%20report%20to%20be%20tabled%20with%20members%20of%20Parliament%20in%20the%20House%20of%20Commons%20to%20determine%20a%20course%20of%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20requirements%20of%20the%20Standing%20Order%2C%20Rishi%20Sunak%20acknowledged%20and%20apologised%20for%20the%20breach%20of%20the%20rules.%20%26quot%3BI%20apologise%20for%20these%20inadvertent%20errors%20and%20confirm%20acceptance%20of%20your%20proposal%20for%20rectification%2C%26quot%3B%20Rishi%20Sunak%20wrote%20in%20his%20letter%20to%20the%20Commissioner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20welcome%20your%20confirmation%20that%20your%20investigation%20related%20to%20declarations%20of%20interests%3B%20there%20is%20no%20question%20that%20I%20correctly%20registered%20my%20wife's%20shareholding%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20also%20grateful%20that%20during%20our%20helpful%20discussion%2C%20you%20accepted%20that%20my%20response%20during%20the%20Liaison%20Committee%20hearing%20on%20March%2028%2C%202023%20complied%20with%20the%20rules%20on%20declaration%2C%20given%20that%20at%20that%20time%2C%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20of%20the%20connection%20between%20Koru%20Kids%20and%20the%20Childminder%20Grants%20Scheme%20policy.%20It%20was%20only%20after%20the%20hearing%20that%20I%20became%20aware%20of%20the%20link%2C%20as%20set%20out%20in%20my%20subsequent%20letter%20to%20Sir%20Bernard%2C%20the%20Chair%20of%20the%20Liaison%20Committee%2C%20dated%20April%204%2C%202023%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20correspondence%2C%20the%20British%20Indian%20leader%20also%20noted%20that%20should%20such%20a%20scenario%20arise%20again%2C%20he%20acknowledges%20a%20duty%20to%20write%20to%20the%20committee%20after%20an%20appearance%20before%20a%20parliamentary%20appearance%20to%20correct%20the%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20accept%20and%20once%20again%20apologise%20that%20my%20letter%20to%20the%20Liaison%20Committee%20on%204%20April%202023%20was%20not%20sufficiently%20expansive%2C%20as%20it%20confused%20the%20language%20of%20registration%20and%20declaration%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20had%20dominated%20the%20headlines%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20Spring%20Budget%20in%20March%2C%20which%20included%20a%20pilot%20scheme%20of%20incentive%20payments%20of%20600%20pounds%20for%20childminders%20joining%20the%20profession%2C%20a%20sum%20that%20doubles%20to%201%2C200%20pounds%20if%20they%20sign%20up%20through%20an%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKoru%20Kids%20was%20one%20of%20six%20childminder%20agencies%20in%20England%20listed%20on%20the%20government's%20website%20when%20the%20policy%20was%20announced%2C%20and%20Akshata%20Murty%20was%20listed%20as%20a%20shareholder%20in%20the%20most%20recently%20filed%20paperwork%20for%20the%20business%20on%20Companies%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20at%20a%20Commons%20Liaison%20Committee%20hearing%20if%20he%20had%20any%20interest%20to%20declare%20when%20talking%20about%20how%20the%20policy%20was%20formed%2C%20Rishi%20Sunak%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BNo%2C%20all%20my%20disclosures%20are%20declared%20in%20the%20normal%20way.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692871020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-08%2Fd1qg2pik_rishi-sunak-akshata-murty_625x300_14_August_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frishi-sunak-apologises-for-iinadvertent-code-breach-over-wife-akshata-murtys-shares-4325204%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rishi%20Sunak%20has%20apologised%20to%20the%20UK%20parliamentary%20watchdog%20after%20an%20investigation%20concluded%20that%20the%20British%20Prime%20Minister's%20failure%20to%20declare%20wife%20Akshata%20Murty's%20relevant%20business%20interest%20arose%20%26quot%3Bout%20of%20confusion%26quot%3B%20and%20was%20%26quot%3Binadvertent%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frishi-sunak-apologises-for-iinadvertent-code-breach-over-wife-akshata-murtys-shares-4325204%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frishi-sunak-apologises-for-iinadvertent-code-breach-over-wife-akshata-murtys-shares-4325204%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frishi-sunak-apologises-for-iinadvertent-code-breach-over-wife-akshata-murtys-shares-4325204%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22British%20Trade%20Secretary%20to%20launch%20UK-India%20campaign%20during%20her%20G20%20visit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22publis