th%20co-hosts%20Pakistan%20squaring%20off%20against%20Nepal%20in%20the%20opening%20match.%20India%20will%20open%20their%20campaign%20against%20the%20arch-rivals%20Pakistan%20on%20September%202%20in%20Kandy.%C2%A0While%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%20was%20picked%20as%20the%20frontline%20spinner%20for%20the%20Asia%20Cup%2C%20the%20other%20spin%20options%20in%20the%20squad%20are%20all-rounders%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20and%20Axar%20Patel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAustralia%20have%20played%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%20very%20well.%20Yuzvendra%20Chahal%20should%20have%20got%20a%20chance.%20He%20is%20a%20match-winning%20bowler.%20Ashwin%20is%20someone%20who%20has%20taken%20500-600%20wickets...%20he%20knows%20how%20to%20take%20wickets.%20We%20did%20not%20play%20him%20in%20the%20WTC%20final%2C%20the%20team%20management%20knows%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20Lal%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Ghavri%20backed%20Ashwin%20for%20the%20upcoming%20World%20Cup%2C%20saying%20he%20will%20be%20vital%20in%20Indian%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20Ashwin%20supposed%20to%20prove%20after%20taking%20712%20international%20wickets%3F%20He%20has%20not%20been%20treated%20well%20despite%20being%20a%20senior%20player%2C%26quot%3B%20Ghavri%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAshwin%20is%20a%20quality%20player%20and%20he%20should%20have%20been%20selected%20for%20the%20Asia%20Cup.%20He%20will%20be%20a%20key%20bowler%20in%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20on%20Indian%20pitches%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELal%20questioned%20the%20fitness%20of%20the%20players%20such%20as%20KL%20Rahul%20and%20Shreyas%20Iyer%2C%20who%20are%20coming%20back%20from%20long%20injury%20layoffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMore%20or%20less%20it%20is%20the%20same%20team%20which%20we%20were%20all%20thinking%20about.%20The%20only%20concern%20is%20their%20fitness%20because%20both%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20and%20the%20World%20Cup%20are%20big%20events%20and%20level%20of%20fitness%20is%20very%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20are%20not%20fit%20physically%20then%20you%20are%20not%20mentally%20fit%20either%20%E2%80%94%20injuries%20always%20worry%20you.%20Hope%20the%20selectors%20have%20taken%20care%20of%20that.%26quot%3B%20Ghavri%20said%20India%20should%20have%20picked%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20instead%20of%20Tilak%20Varma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYashasvi%20did%20very%20well%20in%20the%20West%20Indies.%20He's%20in%20good%20form%20and%20given%20the%20way%20he%20has%20been%20performing%2C%20he%20should%20have%20been%20in%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20team.%20He%20has%20a%20bright%20future%20with%20Team%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverybody%20is%20rating%20Varma%20very%20highly%2C%20but%20where%20is%20the%20performance%3F%20I%20hope%20he%20does%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVarma%20was%20rewarded%20for%20his%20strong%20performances%20on%20the%20tour%20of%20the%20West%20Indies%20with%20a%20spot%20in%20the%20squad%20for%20the%20upcoming%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20young%20batter%20is%20in%20line%20to%20make%20his%20ODI%20debut%2C%20having%20made%20waves%20in%20the%20domestic%20circuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20PTI%20Inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692870540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-10%2Flh34pii_ravichandran-ashwin-instagram_625x300_21_October_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fr-ashwin-yuzvendra-chahal-should-have-been-selected-in-india-squad-feel-former-cricketers-4318012%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22All-rounder%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20and%20leg-spinner%20Yuzvendra%20Chahal%20were%20not%20named%20in%20the%2018-member%20squad%20of%20Team%20India%20for%20the%20Asia%20Cup%202023.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fr-ashwin-yuzvendra-chahal-should-have-been-selected-in-india-squad-feel-former-cr