Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20BRICS%20nations%20have%20expanded%20the%20group%20by%20inviting%20six%20other%20countries%20%E2%80%93%20three%20from%20the%20Gulf%2C%20two%20from%20Africa%20and%20one%20from%20Latin%20America%20%E2%80%93%20to%20be%20full%20members%20on%20Thursday%2C%20August%2024.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnnouncing%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20BRICS%20summit%20in%20Johannesburg%2C%20South%20African%20President%20Cyril%20Ramaphosa%20said%20that%20the%20leaders%20had%20reached%20a%20consensus%20on%20the%20expansion%20guidelines%20and%20agreed%20to%20the%20admission%20of%20six%20countries.%20The%20leaders%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fbrics-nations-agree-expansion-discuss-national-currency-trade%5C%22%3Eannounced%20on%20Wednesday%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20members%20had%20agreed%20on%20expansion%2C%20which%20was%20the%20main%20agenda%20of%20the%2015th%20summit.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20decided%20to%20invite%20the%20Argentine%20Republic%2C%20the%20Arab%20Republic%20of%20Egypt%2C%20the%20Federal%20Republic%20of%20Ethiopia%2C%20the%20Islamic%20Republic%20of%20Iran%2C%20the%20Kingdom%20of%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20to%20become%20full%20members%20of%20BRICS.%20The%20membership%20will%20take%20effect%20from%20January%201%2C%202024%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20at%20a%20joint%20press%20appearance%20with%20all%20the%20five%20current%20members%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20group%20evolved%20from%20a%20paper%20by%20Goldman%20Sachs%2C%20which%20gave%20the%20term%20%E2%80%98BRIC%E2%80%99%20for%20a%20group%20of%20four%20developing%20economies%20that%20had%20the%20potential%20to%20attract%20substantial%20investment.%20The%20first%20formal%20summit%20of%20leaders%20of%20Brazil%2C%20Russia%2C%20India%20and%20China%2C%20was%20held%20in%20Yekaterinburg%20in%20Russia%20in%202009.%20South%20Africa%20joined%20the%20group%20to%20expand%20the%20grouping%20to%20BRICS%20in%202011.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERamaphosa%20noted%20that%20this%20was%20just%20the%20first%20round%20of%20expansion%20of%20BRICS.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20five%20BRICS%20countries%2C%20we%20have%20reached%20an%20agreement%20on%20guiding%20principles%20standards%20criteria%20and%20procedures%20of%20the%20BRICS%20expansion%20process%20which%20has%20been%20in%20discussion%20for%20quite%20a%20while.%20We%20have%20consensus%20on%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20this%20process%20and%20other%20phases%20will%20follow%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongratulating%20the%20new%20members%2C%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20has%20always%20supported%20the%20expansion%20of%20BRICS.%20India%20has%20always%20believed%20that%20adding%20new%20members%20will%20strengthen%20BRICS%20as%20an%20organisation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20walked%20into%20the%20press%20conference%20with%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPutin%2C%20who%20once%20again%20addressed%20the%20summit%20via%20a%20video%20message%2C%20congratulated%20the%20new%20members%20and%20said%20the%20group%20would%20work%20to%20expand%20the%20influence%20of%20BRICS%20in%20the%20world.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20referring%20to%20the%20establishment%20of%20practical%20work%20with%20new%20members%20of%20the%20organisation%20and%20with%20those%20who%20will%20work%20in%20the%20BRICS%20sphere%20as%20outreaches%2C%20with%20our%20partners%20who%20pay%20attention%20to%20each%20other%20cooperation%20with%20our%20organization%20and%20would%20like%20to%20work%20with%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20according%20to%20a%20machine%20translation%20of%20his%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20least%2022%20countries%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-brics-22-countries-expansion-stakes%5C%22%3Ehad%20formally%20applied%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20join%20the%20grouping%2C