0at%20all%20levels%20have%20deteriorated%20due%20to%20tensions%20on%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20(LAC).%20The%20two%20sides%20have%20held%2019%20rounds%20of%20talks%20so%20far%20to%20address%20the%20boundary%20issues%20in%20eastern%20Ladakh%20since%202020%2C%20post%20the%20Chinese%20aggression%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20arrived%20in%20South%20Africa%20for%20the%2015th%20BRICS%20Summit%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opening%20day%20of%20the%20summit%20in%20Johannesburg%20was%20witness%20to%20the%20BRICS%20Business%20Forum%20Leaders'%20Dialogue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20address%20at%20the%20BRICS%20Business%20Forum%20Leaders'%20Dialogue%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20India%20will%20soon%20be%20a%205%20trillion%20dollar%20economy%20and%20in%20the%20coming%20years%20will%20be%20the%20growth%20engine%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi's%20special%20message%20to%20the%20dialogue%20was%20that%20mutual%20trust%20and%20transparency%20can%20help%20create%20a%20big%20impact%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20Global%20South.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20in-person%20BRICS%20Summit%20after%20three%20consecutive%20years%20of%20virtual%20meetings%20owing%20to%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20on%2C%20on%20the%20second%20day%2C%20at%20the%20open%20plenary%20session%20of%20the%2015th%20BRICS%20Summit%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20India%20had%20given%20a%20lot%20of%20importance%20to%20the%20countries%20of%20Global%20South%20under%20its%20G20%20Presidency%20and%20lauded%20South%20Africa%20for%20the%20initiative%20as%20the%20chair%20of%20the%20BRICS%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20welcome%20the%20move%20to%20give%20special%20importance%20to%20the%20countries%20of%20the%20Global%20South%20in%20BRICS%20under%20the%20chairmanship%20of%20South%20Africa.%20This%20is%20not%20just%20the%20aspiration%2C%20but%20also%20the%20need%20of%20the%20present%20times.%20India%20has%20also%20given%20importance%20to%20this%20subject%20