day%20Khakha%2C%20an%20official%20in%20the%20Delhi%20government%E2%80%99s%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%20(WCD)%20department%2C%20was%20sent%20to%20a%2014-day%20judicial%20custody%20along%20with%20his%20wife%20Seema%20Rani%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20August%2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%2C%20the%20girl%20began%20to%20live%20with%20the%20accused%2C%20whom%20she%20referred%20to%20as%20uncle%2C%20following%20the%20death%20of%20her%20father.%20The%20girl%20said%20that%20she%20moved%20along%20with%20her%20mother%20to%20live%20with%20her%20uncle%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20as%20they%20were%20%E2%80%9Cdepressed%E2%80%9D%20due%20to%20her%20father%E2%80%99s%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20went%20to%20my%20uncle%E2%80%99s%20house%20after%20the%20(father%E2%80%99s)%20death%20to%20divert%20my%20mind%20and%20started%20attending%20online%20classes%20from%20there.%20From%20November%202020%20to%20January%202021%2C%20uncle%20raped%20me%E2%80%A6%20aunty%20was%20strict%20and%20would%20hit%20me%20when%20I%20would%20score%20less%20marks.%20The%20last%20time%20he%20sexually%20assaulted%20me%20was%20in%20January%202021%20and%20then%20I%20missed%20my%20period.%20Aunty%20said%20that%20they%20will%20get%20an%20abortion%20done%20since%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20first%20month%E2%80%A6%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20tell%20my%20mother%20anything%2C%20thinking%20she%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20believe%20(me).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20coming%20days%2C%20the%20police%20will%20question%20the%20family%20of%20the%20accused%20and%20their%20friends%20and%20neighbours.%20The%20police%20so%20far%20have%20prepared%20a%20list%20of%2010%20witnesses%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692862152000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F24125734%2FSandeep-Mahajan-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmultiple-medical-tests-conducted-on-delhi-govt-official-accused