n1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20Delhi%20court%20has%20dropped%20charges%20of%20murder%20and%20criminal%20conspiracy%20against%20former%20Congress%20leader%20Sajjan%20Kumar%20in%20two%201984%20riots%20cases.%20It%20has%20framed%20charges%20of%C2%A0rioting%20with%20deadly%20weapons%2C%20promoting%20enmity%20between%20different%20groups%2C%20and%20attempting%20to%20commit%20culpable%20homicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2F1984-riots-court-drops-murder-criminal-conspiracy-charges-sajjan-kumar-8906278%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20in%202015%2C%20a%20special%20investigation%20team%20(SIT)%20had%20registered%20two%20FIRs%20against%20Kumar%20based%20on%20complaints%20of%20violence%20in%20Janakpuri%20and%20Vikaspuri%20during%20the%20anti-Sikh%20violence%20of%201984.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20new%20SIT%20had%20been%20formed%20in%202015%2C%20by%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry.%20In%202018%2C%20two%20men%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdelhi%2Fa-first-for-sit-two-convicted-for-1984-killings%2Farticleshow%2F66627391.cms%5C%22%3Econvicted%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20SIT%E2%80%99s%20investigations%2C%20marking%20the%20first%20arrests%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20SIT%E2%80%99s%20probes.%20Sajjan%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20counsel%20has%20claimed%20in%20court%20that%20the%20formation%20of%20this%20SIT%20is%20illegal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Janakpuri%20FIR%20concerned%20the%20deaths%20of%20one%20Sohan%20Singh%20and%20his%20son-in-law%20Avtar%20Singh.%20The%20Vikaspuri%20FIR%20was%20on%20the%20attack%20on%20Gurcharan%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20set%20ablaze%2C%20sustained%20grievous%20injuries%20and%20remained%20bedridden%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20his%20life.%20These%20incidents%20occurred%20on%20November%201%20and%202%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20communal%20violence%20had%20broken%20out%20after%20the%20assassination%20of%20then%20prime%20minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20on%20October%2031%2C%201984%20by%20her%20two%20Sikh%20bodyguards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAllegations%20contained%20in%20this%20consolidated%20chargesheet%2C%20as%20already%20discussed%2C%20do%20not%20make%20out%20a%20prima%20facie%20case%20for%20the%20commission%20of%20the%20offence%20of%20criminal%20conspiracy%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Rouse%20Avenue%20court%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EExpress%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20cited%20the%20fact%20that%20Kumar%20was%20not%20present%20at%20the%20scene%20of%20the%20crimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20rioting%20with%20deadly%20weapons%2C%20promoting%20enmity%20between%20different%20groups%2C%20and%20attempting%20to%20commit%20culpable%20homicide%2C%20Kumar%20was%20also%20charged%20with%20causing%20mischief%20by%20explosive%20substance%20with%20intent%20to%20destroy%20houses.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692860436000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F18160925%2FSajjan1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsajjan-kumar-1984-riots-murder%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%202015%2C%20a%20special%20investigation%20team%20had%20registered%20two%20FIRs%20against%20the%20Congress%20leader%20based%20on%20complaints%20of%20attacks%20in%20Janakpuri%20and%20Vikaspuri%20during%20the%20anti-Sikh%20riots%20of%201984.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsajjan-kumar-1984-riots-murder%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Sounds%20like%20ChatGPT'%3A%20Ramaswamy%20takes%20center%20stage%20at%20GOP%20debate%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692860338000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103012613%2Cimgsize-9476.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fti