20its%20own%20prime%20ministerial%20candidate%2C%20Srettha%2C%20a%20wealthy%20property%20developer%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fthailand-new-prime-minister-srettha-thavisin-af1ed439685a703cd1c34abf40ae2876%5C%22%3Epolitical%20newcomer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20formed%20a%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FThaiEnquirer%2Fstatus%2F1693607293789855936%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Ecoalition%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20two%20military-aligned%20parties%2C%20the%20Palang%20Pracharath%20Party%20and%20Ruam%20Thai%20Sang%20Chart%20Party%2C%20and%20a%20range%20of%20others.%20This%20gave%20Srettha%20the%20support%20he%20needed%20from%20the%20military-appointed%20senators%20to%20win%20the%20prime%20ministership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Move%20Forward%20and%20Pheu%20Thai%20had%20been%20vocal%20critics%20of%20the%20former%20military-led%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20two%20parties%20had%20different%20stances%20on%20one%20main%20issue%3A%20Thailand%E2%80%99s%20strict%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fexplainer-why-was-the-winner-of-thailands-election-blocked-from-becoming-prime-minister-209730%5C%22%3El%C3%A8se-majest%C3%A9%3C%2Fa%3E%20law%2C%20which%20punishes%20anyone%20who%20criticises%20the%20king%20or%20other%20senior%20royals%20with%20up%20to%2015%20years%20in%20prison.%20Move%20Forward%20pledged%20to%20reform%20it%2C%20while%20Pheu%20Thai%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nationthailand.com%2Fthailand%2Fpolitics%2F40027410%5C%22%3Ecommitted%3C%2Fa%3E%20not%20to%20change%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20difference%20was%20likely%20a%20key%20determinant%20in%20Move%20Forward%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20victory%2C%20but%20also%20the%20reason%20why%20military%20and%20conservative%20parties%20have%20now%20been%20willing%20to%20support%20Pheu%20Thai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20significant%20party%20to%20vote%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSaksithCNA%2Fstatus%2F1693959822897811874%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Eagainst%3C%2Fa%3E%20Srettha%20in%20the%20parliament%20election%20was%20Move%20Forward%20and%20its%20149%20MPs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20secretary-general%20of%20Move%20Forward%20said%20the%20party%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FThaiEnquirer%2Fstatus%2F1693859291638460500%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Eopposed%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20new%20coalition%20because%20it%20refused%20to%20be%20complicit%20in%20returning%20military-aligned%20parties%20to%20government%2C%20even%20one%20led%20by%20Pheu%20Thai.%20He%20argued%20this%20would%20perpetuate%20the%20notion%20that%20Thailand%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cultimate%20power%E2%80%9D%20belonged%20in%20the%20unelected%20Senate%20rather%20than%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20happens%20now%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20no%20coincidence%20that%20Thaksin%20arrived%20on%20the%20day%20his%20party%20returned%20to%20power%2C%20and%20the%20foundations%20are%20already%20being%20set%20for%20his%20early%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20medical%20check-up%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Corrections%20said%20Thaksin%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FThaiEnquirer%2Fstatus%2F1693877188175798273%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Efive%20medical%20conditions%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20an%20ischemic%20heart%20muscle%2C%20chronic%20pulmonary%20inflammation%2C%20high%20blood%20pressure%2C%20degenerated%20spine%20and%20abnormal%20posture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20numerous%20routes%20for%20Thaksin%20to%20be%20released%20from%20prison%2C%20but%20the%20most%20obvious%20one%2C%20due%20to%20his%20age%20of%2074%20and%20these%20reported%20health%20conditions%2C%20is%20on%20medical%20grounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20Thaksin%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2FidINIndia-31110520071225%5C%22%3Eprotestations%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20almost%20two%20decades%20that%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20return%20to%20politics%2C%20there%20is%20little%20doubt%20he%20will%20be%20the%20key%20figure%20operating%20behind%20the%20scenes%20in%20the%20Pheu%20Thai%20party%2C%20and%20therefore%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20such%2C%20we%20may%20see%20a%20tussle%20between%20Srettha%20and%20Thaksin%20for%20influence%20in%20the%20party.%20Srettha%20may%20very%20well%20attempt%20to%20project%20the%20image%20that%20he%20is%20his%20own%20man%20and%20not%20beholden%20to%20anyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20being%20years%20away%2C%20the%20next%20election%20could%20also%20be%20fraught%20for%20Pheu%20Thai.%20The%20party%20has%20not%20only%20betrayed%20Move%20Forward%20voters%20with%20its%20actions%20this%20week%2C%20it%20has%20also%20betrayed%20its%20own%20supporters%20who%20believed%20its%20commitment%20to%20keep%20the%20military-aligned%20parties%20out%20of%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Pheu%20Thai%20can%20hold%20the%20unwieldy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F8%2F21%2Fthailands-pheu-thai-to-ally-with-military-rivals-to-form-new-government%5C%22%3E11-party%20coalition%3C%2Fa%3E%20together%20for%20the%20next%20four%20years%2C%20however%2C%20it%20has%20plenty%20of%20time%20to%20convince%20voters%20to%20stick%20with%20it%20at%20the%20next%20election.%20It%20may%20also%20deliver%20enough%20sweeteners%20to%20remain%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20Move%20Forward%E2%80%99s%20supporters%20are%20angry.%20In%20a%20potentially%20ominous%20sign%20for%20Pheu%20Thai%2C%20within%20hours%20of%20Srettha%E2%80%99s%20election%20to%20prime%20minister%2C%20%23NotMyPM%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMayWongCNA%2Fstatus%2F1693983366415303022%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Etrending%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Thailand%E2%80%99s%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20again%2C%20the%20anti-democratic%20forces%20within%20Thailand%E2%80%99s%20elites%20have%20stifled%20the%20will%20of%20the%20people%20and%20we%20may%20be%20entering%20another%20volatile%2