0system%20with%20digital%20learning%20methods%2C%20the%20enrollment%20of%20girls%20increased%20to%20129.%20This%20impact%20encouraged%20us%20to%20understand%20that%20what%20we%20are%20doing%20is%20meaningful%20for%20the%20children%20in%20the%20government%20ecosystem%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20kick%20off%20the%20work%2C%20Abhishek%E2%80%99s%20Muskaan%20Dreams%20signs%20an%20MoU%20(Memorandum%20of%20Understanding)%20with%20the%20state%20governments%20for%20a%20particular%20period.%20Thereafter%2C%20they%20conduct%20in-person%20meetings%20with%20district%20collectors%20who%20help%20them%20select%20government%20schools%20in%20rural%20areas%20based%20on%20the%20power%20availability%20to%20run%20the%20electronic%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20then%20arrange%20meetings%20with%20teachers%20and%20students%20and%20engage%20them%20in%20discussions%20about%20the%20benefits%20and%20opportunities%20that%20lie%20ahead.%20It%20helps%20build%20enthusiasm%20and%20commitment%20among%20teachers%20and%20students%20and%20ensure%20their%20active%20involvement%20in%20the%20implementation%20phase%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20collaborating%20with%20schools%2C%20we%20provide%20them%20with%20electronic%20devices%2C%20content%2C%20and%20training%20to%20teachers.%20We%20focus%20on%20improving%20the%20performance%20of%20children%20in%20Maths%20and%20Science%20because%20there%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20these%20subject%20teachers%20in%20the%20government%20schools%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fg0HA2PbezIc%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26autoplay%3D0%26cc_load_policy%3D0%26cc_lang_pref%3D%26iv_load_policy%3D3%26loop%3