e%20maize%2C%20barley%2C%20and%20wheat%20for%20goats%2C%20cows%2C%20buffaloes%2C%20and%20ducks.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20this%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20green%20fodder%20is%20an%20added%20woe.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20farmer%20does%20not%20have%20enough%20land%20to%20grow%20green%20fodder%20on%20their%20own%2C%20they%20are%20forced%20to%20purchase%20expensive%20fodder%20from%20the%20market.%20The%20green%20fodder%20grown%20using%20traditional%20methods%20costs%20Rs%208%E2%80%9314%20per%20kg%20whereas%20that%20grown%20hydroponically%20costs%20Rs%202%20per%20kg%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20its%20benefits%20of%20conserving%20land%20and%20water%2C%20the%20main%20drawback%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F265317%2Futtar-pradesh-hydroponics-farm-home-grows-vegetables-fruits-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehydroponic%20technique%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20its%20expensive%20cost.%20Aswhin%20says%20a%20one-tonne%20unit%20costs%20up%20to%20Rs%2016%20lakh.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20setups%20require%20air%20conditioners%2C%20ozonators%2C%20and%20UV%20and%20RO%20systems.%20This%20increases%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20unit.%20I%20wanted%20to%20reduce%20its%20price%20so%20that%20many%20farmers%20can%20adopt%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20multiple%20trials%20and%20errors%2C%20Ashwin%20developed%20a%20low-cost%20economical%20model%20that%20cost%20Rs%203%20lakh%20on%20average.%20This%20model%20could%20be%20replicated%20across%20various%20geographies%20in%20the%20country.%20Ashwin%20worked%20on%20vital%20parameters%20like%20temperature%20and%20humidity%20required%20to%20promote%20the%20growth%20of%20green%20fodder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20regulate%20temperature%2C%20he%20replaced%20air%20conditioners%20with%20his%20%E2%80%98fan-and-pad%E2%80%99%20based%20cooling%20system%20that%20uses%20exhaust%20fans%20to%20pu