ing%20to%20the%20pollution%2C%20traffic%20and%20commotion.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20precisely%20this%20thought%20that%20shaped%20his%20journey%20of%20starting%20Meena%20Bagh%20Homes%20on%20his%20ancestral%20plot%20of%20land%20in%20Himachal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FIMG-20230811-WA0019-1691756057.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Made%20with%20traditional%20kath%20kuni%20architecture%2C%20the%20homestay%20is%20resilient%20to%20the%20extreme%20climates%20seen%20in%20the%20region%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FIMG-20230811-WA0019-1691756057.jpg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FIMG-20230811-WA0019-1691756057-300x214.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FIMG-20230811-WA0019-1691756057-500x356.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FIMG-20230811-WA0019-1691756057-768x547.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FIMG-20230811-WA0019-1691756057-150x107.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327064%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22912%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMade%20with%20traditional%20kath%20kuni%20architecture%2C%20the%20homestay%20is%20resilient%20to%20the%20extreme%20climates%20seen%20in%20the%20region%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Sanjay%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20thing%20that%20gave%20impetus%20to%20Sanjay%E2%80%99s%20burning%20desire%20to%20return%20to%20the%20hills%20was%20the%20craving%20to%20be%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F90205%2F10-sustainable-homestays-india%2F%5C%22%3Eproximity%20to%20nature%3C%2Fa%3E